{"tid":47223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京故宮推「朕的手機」 18K鍍金賣$2.2萬","createTime":"2016-12-20T07:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T08:47:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a12391821d2172aee02ffb1d4ecba90c663e5e2b","tid":47223,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4PimB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4PimB6.jpg&h=adc7ae74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n土豪氣息十足！北京故宮推出手機，18K鍍金雕龍外殼，號稱「朕的手機」！承惠19,999元人民幣（下同‧約2.2萬港元）。網民提出疑問，不知國家主席習近平有沒有一部呢？<br />\n<br />\n「朕的手機，邀您品鑒！」故宮文化傳播有限公司，聯合8848鈦金手機和設計師勞倫斯&middot;許共同打造的故宮手機昨日正式亮相，背部18K鍍金加上鏤空浮雕工藝，配上小牛皮材質，有明黃（即金色）、朱紅、玄黑、石青四色版本，趕在農曆新年前面世。不過價格不菲，要19,999元，據說國內限量999部。<br />\n<br />\n手機配備5寸1080p螢幕，八核處理器，記憶體組合是4GB RAM和128GB ROM，主攝像鏡頭2,100萬像素（前置300萬像素），支援雙卡雙待全網通，內置掌上故宮App，手機壁紙是故宮的五福捧壽，祥雲無盡等吉祥圖案以及二十四節氣攝影作品。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊科技<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56068468&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161220\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56068468%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161220&d=LokDDrC3299haMjCSi6EvGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=ede013f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56068468%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161220&h=56266d2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56068468&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161220</a>"},{"pid":"50540042140347312e3bd57ba7ed1a939e7f31c8","tid":47223,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"全世界真係得強國用金色可以用得咁柒咁俗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688180b9ca8552b7f2f552d5d6be54c61c1c525c","tid":47223,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"